        "created_at": "2018-10-29T17:26:55.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>had 08 Butteaux last night. A disappointment in the context of the 10 and 04. A bit dilute and lacking vibrant acidity, though smelled nice and had decent fruit. Not Chablis in character, more generic.</p>",
        "post_number": 5,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 9,
